<div class="info">
    <h3>Delivery</h3>
    <blockquote>I have received a faulty/damaged item in my order, what should I do?</blockquote>
    <p>If you believe you have had faulty/damaged items delivered to you please call us straight 
    away on +44 (0) 151 676 2211.</p>
    <blockquote>I have/haven&rsquo;t received an 
    item I did/didn&rsquo;t order, what should I do?</blockquote>
    <p>If you believe you have received or not 
    received an item incorrectly please call us straight 
    away on +44 (0) 151 676 2211.</p>
    <h3>UK Delivery Information</h3>
    <p>The cost of delivery will be as stated on the 
    website at the time of the order. A specific time 
    slot can unfortunately not be specified at this time. 
    </p><br/>
    <h3>Returns</h3>
    <blockquote>What is your returns policy?</blockquote>
    <p>We offer a full refund within 7 days of you receiving 
    the item as long as item is in resellable condition and 
    is non perishable. Please call a member of our team on
    +44 (0) 151 656 2211 if you wish to organise a return. </p>
    <h3>Shopping</h3>
    <blockquote>Do I need to create an account 
    to be able to order?</blockquote>
    <p>Yes, every customer must have created an account prior 
    to ordering containing their correct contact details.</p>
    <blockquote>How do I change my account 
    details?</blockquote>
    <p>You can change your account details by clicking on the 
    relevant option in the login section of each page on the site.
    This can be found on the right hand side of every page. 
    Please note, you must be logged in to change your details.
    Alternatively, you can contact a member of our team on 
    +44 (0) 151 656 2211.</p>
</div>